         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office ¶ Melbourne 5 Feby 1884 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ With reference to the Circular of the 2nd inst. from the Premier's Office, a copy of which has been forwarded to you, ¶  requiring the prepa...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.02.05</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 427, pp. 1229-30, unit 65, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office of Victoria</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Document is a circular sent to 16 branches within the Chief Secretary's Department.</p>
               </note>Chief Secretary's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 5 Feby 1884</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With reference to the Circular of the 2nd inst. from the Premier's Office, a copy of which has been forwarded to you,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Circular not found.</p>
               </note> requiring the preparation of certain returns under Section 20 of the Public Service Act 1883, I am directed to inform you that the Public Service Board have called for the undermentioned additional information, and to require that it may be prepared and forwarded to this office with the principal returns, with the least possible delay.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">1</hi>
               </seg> "A supplementary return (in form A annexed) giving a summary of the number of persons employed at each rate of salary in each <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">division</hi>
               </seg> of each <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">branch</hi>
               </seg> of your Department."</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">2</hi>
               </seg> "A similar summary in respect of each branch (in form B annexed)</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">3</hi>
               </seg> A return showing the age last birthday, &amp; date of birthday, of each employé (this may be furnished in an additional column on the forms already supplied as shown in form C annexed).</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be, Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>T. R. Wilson<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M’s reply dated 8 February 1884, reporting the ages and salaries of the officers in his department, was registered at the Chief Secretary’s Office on 9 February (B84/1411, VPRS 1168, Public Record Office, Victoria) but has not been found.</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">The Government Botanist</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">&amp;c <space unit="chars" quantity="5"/>&amp;c <space unit="chars" quantity="5"/>&amp;c</p>
         </div>
      </body>
